casebody.data:
Wednesday, January 12, 2000

MOTION DOCKET

99-2154. Buelow v. Vocational Guidance Serv.

Cuyahoga App. No. 74965. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. On January 6, 2000, appellee filed a memorandum in response that was due January 5, 2000. S.Ct.Prac.R. XIV(1)(C) prohibits the filing of a memorandum in response that is not timely. Accordingly,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that the appellee’s memorandum in response be, and hereby is, stricken.
